  "doc_id": "17352",
  "text": "Extracts of optic nerves from 3-5-wk-old rats were prepared as previously described [CITATION_1] except that 2 M NaC1 was used. The extracts were dialyzed extensively against 150 mM NaC1, centrifuged at 80000 g for 30 min to remove material that had precipitated, and then stored at -70\"C. We refer to this extract as 2M-ONE.",
  "correct_citation": {
